### ============================================================
### ACTIVITY CRUD OPERATIONS
### ============================================================

### 1. Get All Activities
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/api/activity/get-all
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get List Activities with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/api/activity/get-list?page=1&limit=10&search=
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Get Select Activities (for dropdown)
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/api/activity/get-select
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 4. Get Activity by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/api/activity/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 5. Create New Activity
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/api/activity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "ACT001",
  "name": "Hội thảo kỹ năng mềm 2024",
  "start_date": "2024-12-20T08:00:00Z",
  "end_date": "2024-12-20T17:00:00Z",
  "is_required": true,
  "location": "Hội trường A - Tầng 3",
  "description": "Hội thảo về phát triển kỹ năng mềm cho sinh viên năm cuối"
}

###

### 6. Update Activity
PUT http://localhost:3000/v1/api/activity/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hội thảo kỹ năng mềm 2024 - Updated",
  "start_date": "2024-12-21T08:00:00Z",
  "end_date": "2024-12-21T17:00:00Z",
  "location": "Hội trường B - Tầng 5"
}

###

### 7. Delete Activity
DELETE http://localhost:3000/v1/api/activity/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 8. Delete Many Activities
DELETE http://localhost:3000/v1/api/activity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

